Ghana’s Mills to Retain Mahama as 2012 Running Mate, Joy Online Reports

-- B y   E k o w   D o n t o h
-- 
2011-08-04T17:33:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/ghana-s-mills-to-retain-mahama-as-2012-running-mate-joy-online-reports.html
Ghana’s president, John Atta Mills,
received approval from his National Democratic Congress party to
retain Vice President John Mahama as his running mate in an
election planned for December 2012, Accra-based broadcaster Joy
FM reported today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ekow Dontoh in Johannesburg at 
 edontoh@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net  